prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D watercolor greeting card front. A funny and lighthearted birthday scene on a sunny beach. In the center, Lao Lao (the person on the left from photo 8bea52ef-5c0c-43db-b975-b7dba3d47f04) is relaxing in a beach chair, wearing sunglasses and her light blue sweatshirt and black pants. She has a wide, amused smile, looking down at Jordan (the person on the right from the photo) who is enthusiastically digging a giant hole in the sand beside her chair, kicking up little sprays of sand. Jordan is wearing his tan hoodie and dark pants. The beach is whimsical, with a half-built sandcastle decorated with dog biscuits. A bright beach umbrella sticks out of the sand, and a colorful beach ball sits nearby. The ocean behind them is a beautiful turquoise blue with soft, gentle waves. In the center of the image, floating slightly above the scene, is text written in a beautiful, flowing handwritten cursive script that reads: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!". The overall style is a vibrant watercolor with soft edges, blended colors, and a playful, charming feel.
